{"tid":1674362,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"劉鶴將要求美方撤關稅以換取購買更多農產品","createTime":"2019-10-25T07:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T07:30:01.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a7ee9128d776f4f40d58cc989a1d7f0e88b60e5","tid":1674362,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:20:46.000Z","msg":"路透引述消息指，中美雙方將於周五(25日)討論中國擬增購美國農產品的計劃，而北京將要求美國取消部分現有或計劃實施的關稅。報道指美國貿易代表萊特希澤(Robert Lighthizer)、美國財長努欽(Steven Mnuchin)以及中國副總理劉鶴將於周五通電話，雙方現時正努力達成特朗普在10月11日宣布的第一階段貿易協議，以趕及在下月於智利舉行的峰會上簽署。<br />\n<br />\n至今特朗普僅同意取消於10月15日向2,500億美元中國進口貨加徵關稅，以尋求中國購買更多農產品、開放金融服務市場，以及加強保護知識產權等，但中方預期將要求美國放棄於12月15日向1,560億美元中國貨徵稅，涉及產品包括手提電話、手提電腦及玩具等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中方亦有可能要求美國取消於9月1日生效、向1,250億美元中國貨徵稅的決定。消息人士稱，中國希望美國只向原定的2,500億美元貨品徵稅。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.972274/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.972274%2F2&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTfrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=0c496f39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.972274/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1ef7542d30c980369b737848d195ef3aafdcca","tid":1674362,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:27:32.000Z","msg":"唔好咁多嗲啦鶴一陣又要再傾過"},{"pid":"4f554590828fc2a2245ca0a78ecb98ea4e88e8a2","tid":1674362,"uid":256142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:30:01.000Z","msg":"出外是人質<br />\n回家是condom"}]}